OL,3,CPolice hunt man who may have 'vital
OL,4,Cinformation' about death at skip yard
OL,6,FA man who may have "vital information"
OL,7,Fabout the death of a 34-year-old at a
OL,8,Fskip yard is being hunted by police
OL,9,Fafter he is believed to have fled
OL,10,Fabroad.
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police detectives have
OL,13,Fnamed Bashar Al-Kadah, 30, as someone
OL,14,Fthey want to speak to following the
OL,15,Fdeath of Yadvinder Satnam Singh last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@fO]
