OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772550673
OL,3,CPolice hunt man who may have 'vital
OL,4,Cinformation' about death at skip yard
OL,6,FDetective Constable Cynthia Da Silva
OL,7,Fsaid: "Yadvinder's death was tragic
OL,8,Fand our thoughts remain with his
OL,9,Ffamily and friends.
OL,11,F"We are committed to finding answers
OL,12,Ffor Yadvinder's family and have spent
OL,13,Fthe past six months conducting
OL,14,Fextensive enquiries to identify the
OL,15,Fcircumstances surrounding this awful
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"Despite hundreds of hours of work,
OL,19,Fincluding trawling phone records and
OL,20,Fbanking details, we have been unable
OL,21,Fto locate Al-Kadah.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
