OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772550673
OL,3,CPolice hunt man who may have 'vital
OL,4,Cinformation' about death at skip yard
OL,6,F"We are now calling on anyone who
OL,7,Frecognises him or knows where he is to
OL,8,Fget in touch with police."
OL,10,FTwo men, both aged in their 40s, were
OL,11,Farrested on suspicion of manslaughter
OL,12,Fin August last year and released under
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,16,Fcontact police on 101, quoting
OL,17,Freference 01/7829119/25, or
OL,18,Fanonymously at Crimestoppers on 0800
OL,19,F555 111 or online.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@ZO]
